{"tid":1567261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】港鐵沙田站警民衝突　警機場再拘一女子","createTime":"2019-09-14T03:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T04:02:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38b4ae25953b8c788dbfc4fbdf952263dbb98866","tid":1567261,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙田站上周六（7日）晚發生警民衝突，警方當晚拘捕3名年齡介乎21至27歲男子，分別涉襲警、拒捕、藏有攻擊性武器及阻礙警務人員執行職務。他們已獲准保釋候查，須於10月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在香港國際機場，以涉嫌襲警再拘捕一名45歲女子，她現正被扣留調查，案件由商業罪案調查科人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190914/s00001/1568429471917/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e6%b2%99%e7%94%b0%e7%ab%99%e8%ad%a6%e6%b0%91%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81-%e8%ad%a6%e6%a9%9f%e5%a0%b4%e5%86%8d%e6%8b%98%e4%b8%80%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190914%2Fs00001%2F1568429471917%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2594%25b0%25e7%25ab%2599%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%2586%258d%25e6%258b%2598%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%25ad%2590&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=4e134628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190914%2Fs00001%2F1568429471917%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2594%25b0%25e7%25ab%2599%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%2586%258d%25e6%258b%2598%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%25ad%2590&h=09f052f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ne